{"word":"G73 - ἀγών - agṓn - ag-one' - Conflict","slug":"G73","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀγών</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>agṓn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ag-one'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Conflict"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B3;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03BD; - ago&#x0304;n</b> - <i>ag-one'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G71\">G71</a>; properly a place of <i>assembly</i> (as if <i>led</i>), that is, (by implication) a <i>contest</i> (held there); figuratively an <i>effort</i> or <i>anxiety:</i> - conflict, contention, fight, race."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1864\">G1864</a>, <a href=\"#/G2610\">G2610</a>, <a href=\"#/G464\">G464</a>, <a href=\"#/G74\">G74</a>, <a href=\"#/G75\">G75</a>"}]}